OL,3,CStudent admits killing his stepdad,
OL,4,Cwho was stabbed 17 times in his own bed
OL,6,FA university student has admitted
OL,7,Fkilling his stepdad after the ex-
OL,8,Fpolice officer was stabbed 17 times in
OL,9,Fhis own bed.
OL,11,FAndrew McDiarmid, a former detective
OL,12,Finspector who served Merseyside Police
OL,13,Ffor 30 years, died aged 64 after being
OL,14,Fattacked inside the family home on
OL,15,FOldfield Way in in January 2022.
OL,17,FHis wife's son Benjamin Moglione has
OL,18,Fbeen standing trial at Crown Court
OL,19,Faccused of his murder.
