OL,3,CStudent admits killing his stepdad,
OL,4,Cwho was stabbed 17 times in his own bed
OL,6,FBut he pleaded guilty to the lesser
OL,7,Fcount of manslaughter on Thursday, on
OL,8,Fthe grounds of diminished
OL,9,Fresponsibility.
OL,11,FOn Friday, the court was told by
OL,12,Fprosecution junior Stephen McNally
OL,13,Fthat this plea would be accepted by
OL,14,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service.
OL,16,FThe jury was therefore instructed to
OL,17,Frecord a not guilty verdict on the
OL,18,Fmurder charge faced by Moglione. He
OL,19,Fwill be sentenced on May 21..
