OL,3,CStudent admits killing his stepdad,
OL,4,Cwho was stabbed 17 times in his own bed
OL,6,FThe Honorary Recorder of Liverpool
OL,7,FJudge Andrew Menary KC, who presided
OL,8,Fwho the trial, said: "In this case,
OL,9,Fthe defendant does not deny that he
OL,10,Fwas responsible for sadly killing his
OL,11,Fstepfather. It seems that - while
OL,12,FBenjamin Moglione's mother was in the
OL,13,Fshower, at a time when he was believed
OL,14,Fto be in bed - he had taken a kitchen
OL,15,Fknife, gone to his stepfather's
OL,16,Fbedroom and stabbed him multiple times
OL,17,Fto the chest and abdomen and in that
OL,18,Fway caused his death.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
