OL,6,FEarlier, a jury of eight men and four
OL,7,Fwomen heard the prosecution's opening
OL,8,Fthat the 23-year-old's mum Alison
OL,9,FMoglione had called 999 at around
OL,10,F8.45pm on January 24 2022 and reported
OL,11,Fthat her son had stabbed her husband.
OL,12,FEmergency services subsequently
OL,13,Fattended the address and found Mr
OL,14,FMcDiarmid lying gravely wounded on top
OL,15,Fof the bed in the couple's bedroom.
