OL,3,CStudent admits killing his stepdad,
OL,4,Cwho was stabbed 17 times in his own bed
OL,6,FHe was said to have "sustained some 17
OL,7,Fwounds to his body", 13 being stab
OL,8,Fwounds and "some described as incised
OL,9,Fwounds". Mr Cole told the court that a
OL,10,Fnumber of these injuries had been
OL,11,F"inflicted with severe force".
OL,13,FMoglione - who suffers from a "number
OL,14,Fof physical and mental health issues,
OL,15,Fin particular epilepsy" - was arrested
OL,16,Fat the scene, and has remained in
OL,17,Fhospital since."
