OL,3,CStudent admits killing his stepdad,
OL,4,Cwho was stabbed 17 times in his own bed
OL,6,FMs Moglione was also arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing Mr McDiarmid's death and
OL,8,Fspent the following two nights in
OL,9,Fcustody. She said of this: "I've never
OL,10,Feven had a parking ticket in my life.
OL,11,FI feel I didn't know, and Andy didn't
OL,12,Fknow, how ill Ben was. This could have
OL,13,Fbeen avoided if we had a good
OL,14,Fneurologist who had put him on the
OL,15,Fright medication."
OL,17,FBenjamin Moglione will be sentenced in
OL,18,FMay.
